title: C Program
description: Learn the C programming language and its fundamental programming concepts. Gain the knowledge to write simple C language applications and undertake future courses that assume some background in computer programming. Topics include variables, data types, functions, control structures, pointers, strings, arrays and dynamic allocation principles. You need access to any programming environment that allows you to write, edit, compile, link and debug a C program.
